2004-03-28  Benjamin Otte  <otte@gnome.org>

	* gst/mpegstream/gstdvddemux.c: (gst_dvd_demux_process_private):
	* gst/mpegstream/gstmpegdemux.c: (gst_mpeg_demux_parse_syshead),
