2004-01-15  David Schleef  <ds@schleef.org>

	* ext/esd/esdsink.c: (gst_esdsink_class_init): Remove property
	that handles osssink fallback.
	* gst/audioconvert/gstaudioconvert.c: (gst_audio_convert_init),
